description:
From Good Girls Scan BL:

Yoh and Komiya, two boys with brother complexes, start pretending to date. Even though it started out as a plan to make their brothers realize their importance, before they knew it, they started enjoying &ldquo;fake dating&rdquo;&hellip; To top things off, Komiya, who starts to find Yoh&rsquo;s pureness irresistibly cute, couldn&rsquo;t help but kiss him?? 

&ldquo;Should I teach you a kiss that&rsquo;ll make you melt?&rdquo; 
&ldquo;I don&rsquo;t mind anything if it&rsquo;s you, Senpai??&rdquo;
